== Competitive record ==
=== FIFA World Cup ===
{{main|Morocco at the FIFA World Cup}}

Morocco's national football team has participated in the [[FIFA World Cup|World Cup]] six times. Their best performance was in the [[2022 FIFA World Cup|2022 tournament]] where they finished in fourth place, becoming the first African nation to reach the semi-finals of the tournament.

